## Installed Dependencies (server/vendor/)
- fastapi, uvicorn, edge-tts — core backend
- pymupdf (fitz) — PDF parsing
- llama-cpp-python — local LLM inference
- torch (CPU build) — required for NLLB-200 translation
- transformers, sentencepiece, sacremoses — NLLB-200 model loading and tokenization
- requests, python-dotenv, httpx — HTTP and config
- elevenlabs, openai — optional TTS/STT alternatives

