## Coding Preferences
- Python 3.11 on backend
- No unnecessary new dependencies — use what's already in vendor/
- Keep endpoints simple and RESTful
- Async where possible (FastAPI async def)
- Print statements for logging (no logging module needed for now)
- Frontend: functional components, hooks only, no class components
- Never use HTML <form> tags in React — use onClick handlers instead
- pip install always goes to server/vendor/ with --target server/vendor
- Never commit server/.env, server/vendor/, or server/models/
